    • Ball

      public Ball​(java.awt.geom.Point2D center, int radiusA, int radiusB, java.awt.Color inner, java.awt.Color border)
      This is the constructor of "Ball" class. This constructor holds the data that required initialization once its object is created.
      Parameters:
      center - This parameter is the position of the ball.
      radiusA - This parameter is the radius of the ball.
      radiusB - This parameter is the radius of the ball.
      inner - This parameter is the inner colour of the ball.
      border - This parameter is the border colour of the ball.
